title: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
headline: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ members who've signed up for this month (January 11 - February 7) will also receive:

— The new Albany Cavalcade XL
— Access to the Vinewood Club Garage
— Exclusive clothing
— 40% off the Tow Truck upgrade for the Salvage Yard
— 20% off Drift Tuning Vehicle Upgrades
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
